(11, NULL, 2, 'Halloween Discount Deals', 'Halloween', NULL, NULL, 'halloween-discount-codes', 'Halloween Discount Codes 2025 – Spooky Deals & Coupons', 'Halloween discount codes, Halloween coupons 2025, Halloween deals, Halloween promo codes, spooky savings,', 'Get ready for the spookiest savings! 🎃 Discover the best Halloween discount codes, coupon deals, and flash sales for 2025. Save big on your favorite brands at Big Saving Hub before they vanish!', 'uploads/1763233743.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763233563.jpg', NULL, 'Get ready for a frightfully good deal! 👻 From October 31 to November 11, Top Code Voucher is conjuring up an exclusive collection of Halloween discount codes & coupon deals you won’t want to miss.', 'Halloween is all about fun — and savings! Top Code Voucher collects the best Halloween promo codes to help you celebrate without overspending.\r\n\r\n* Discounts on costumes, accessories, and party supplies\r\n* Savings on candy, chocolates, and spooky decor\r\n* Fresh, verified codes updated daily\r\n\r\nDon’t let the deals vanish into thin air — grab your Halloween savings before they disappear! 🎃', 1, 1, 95, '2025-10-01 18:31:33', '2025-11-18 10:24:11'),
(12, NULL, 3, 'Black Friday Deals', 'Black Friday', NULL, NULL, 'black-friday-deals', 'Black Friday Deals – Unbeatable Discounts Await!', 'black friday deals, black friday sale, black friday discounts, best black friday offers, holiday shopping deals, cyber week savings', 'Grab the hottest Black Friday deals and massive discounts across top brands. Limited-time offers you don’t want to miss – shop smart and save big today!', 'uploads/1763233765.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763233626.jpg', NULL, 'Get ready for the biggest shopping event of the year! 🛍️ Top Code Voucher brings you exclusive Black Friday deals & coupons with massive discounts on fashion, electronics, home essentials, and more.', 'Black Friday is here, and Top Code Voucher is your go-to destination for unbeatable savings. From electronics and gadgets to clothing, beauty, and home essentials, we’ve gathered the best coupons and promo codes from top brands.\r\n\r\n* Verified codes & daily flash deals\r\n* Discounts across all major categories\r\n* Easy-to-use coupons for maximum savings\r\n\r\nDon’t miss out — shop smart this Black Friday with Top Code Voucher!', 1, 1, 51, '2025-10-01 22:39:18', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(13, NULL, 4, 'Thanksgiving Day Deals', 'Thanksgiving', NULL, NULL, 'thanksgiving-day-deals', 'Thanksgiving Day Event – Celebrate with Joy & Deals', 'thanksgiving day event, thanksgiving celebration, thanksgiving deals, holiday event, family thanksgiving, thanksgiving party, thanksgiving sales', 'Join the Thanksgiving Day Event filled with family fun, festive vibes, and special offers. Celebrate gratitude with joy, food, and unforgettable moments!', 'uploads/1763233987.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763233694.jpg', NULL, 'Celebrate this Thanksgiving with amazing savings! 🍂 Find the best Thanksgiving Day coupon codes and discounts for food, fashion, gifts, and more at Top Code Voucher.', 'Thanksgiving isn’t just about turkey — it’s about great deals too! At Top Code Voucher, we’ve handpicked Thanksgiving coupon codes to make your holiday shopping easier and more affordable.\r\n\r\n* Save on groceries, cooking essentials, and dining\r\n* Discounts on fashion, gifts, and home decor\r\n* Exclusive codes from popular retailers\r\n\r\nMake this Thanksgiving extra special without overspending. Check back daily for fresh, limited-time coupon codes!', 1, 0, 26, '2025-10-01 22:56:56', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(14, NULL, 5, 'Christmas Deals', 'Christmas', NULL, NULL, 'christmas-deals', 'Christmas Deals Event – Save Big This Holiday', 'christmas deals online event, christmas discounts, holiday sales, christmas offers, online christmas shopping, festive deals, holiday savings', 'Discover the Christmas Deals Event packed with festive discounts, exclusive offers, and holiday savings. Shop smart and celebrate with joy!', 'uploads/1763234158.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234132.jpg', NULL, 'It’s the season of giving — and saving! 🎅 Top Code Voucher brings you the best Christmas deals and coupons for gifts, fashion, electronics, and more.', 'Christmas shopping can be expensive, but with Top Code Voucher\'s exclusive Christmas coupons, you’ll keep your wallet merry and bright.\r\n\r\n* Huge savings on Christmas gifts for everyone\r\n* Special discounts on clothing, electronics, toys, and holiday decor\r\n* Verified working codes updated daily\r\n\r\nThis holiday season, spread joy without breaking the bank. Shop smarter with Top Code Voucher Christmas Deals!', 1, 0, 22, '2025-10-01 23:14:03', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(15, NULL, 6, 'Monthly Discount Offers', 'Monthly', NULL, NULL, 'monthly-discount-offers', 'Monthly Discount Offers – Save More Every Time', 'monthly discount offers, monthly deals, special offers, discount shopping, monthly sales, online discounts, exclusive offers, best savings', 'Don’t miss the Monthly Discount Offers packed with exclusive deals, huge savings, and limited-time discounts to help you shop smarter every month!', 'uploads/1763234221.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234201.jpg', NULL, 'Why wait for the holidays? 🎁 Top Code Voucher offers monthly discount coupons and deals to help you save all year round.', 'Savings don’t have to be seasonal at Top Code Voucher, you’ll find monthly discount offers from top online stores.\r\n\r\n* Fresh coupon codes added every month\r\n* Discounts across fashion, electronics, travel, food & more\r\n* Verified and active codes to save you time and money\r\n\r\nBookmark this page and check back every month for updated offers — because there’s always a reason to save!', 1, 0, 22, '2025-10-01 23:28:58', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(16, NULL, 7, 'Valentine\'s Day Deals Event', 'Valentines', NULL, NULL, 'valentines-day-deals', 'Valentine\'s Day Deals Event – Love Big, Save Bigger', 'Valentine\'s Day deals event, Valentine’s sale, Valentine’s Day discounts, romantic gifts offers, Valentine’s shopping deals, love day discounts', 'Celebrate love with the Valentine\'s Day Deals Event! Grab romantic gifts, exclusive offers, and limited-time discounts to make your day extra special.', 'uploads/1763234292.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234270.jpg', NULL, 'Celebrate love with savings! 💘 Top Code Voucher brings you the best Valentine’s Day coupons and deals on gifts, flowers, fashion, and more.', 'Valentine’s Day is all about showing love — without overspending. Top Code Voucher helps you find exclusive Valentine’s Day coupon codes to make gifting easier.\r\n\r\nDiscounts on flowers, chocolates, jewelry, and fashion\r\n\r\nSpecial deals on romantic getaways and dining\r\n\r\nVerified working coupons updated daily\r\n\r\nMake your Valentine’s Day special while keeping your budget intact. 💝', 1, 0, 23, '2025-10-03 16:27:50', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(17, NULL, 8, 'Easter Deals Event', 'Easter', NULL, NULL, 'easter-deal-codes', 'Easter Deals Event – Egg-citing Discounts Await!', 'Easter deals event, Easter discounts, Easter sales, festive offers, holiday shopping deals, Easter special promotions, spring discounts', 'Hop into savings with the Easter Deals Event! Discover egg-citing offers, festive discounts, and special Easter sales to brighten your celebrations.', 'uploads/1763234363.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234344.jpg', NULL, 'Celebrate Easter with savings! 🐣 Find the best Easter deals and coupon codes on gifts, fashion, sweets, and more at Top Code Voucher.', 'Easter is the perfect time for family, celebrations, and savings. At Top Code Voucher, we’ve gathered Easter coupon codes for everything from gifts and fashion to sweets and decor.\r\n\r\n* Save on Easter baskets, chocolates, and candy\r\n* Discounts on clothing, shoes, and accessories\r\n* Verified codes from top online stores\r\n\r\nMake this Easter fun and affordable with Top Code Voucher’s exclusive coupons!', 1, 0, 21, '2025-10-03 16:46:55', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(18, NULL, 9, 'Labor Day Event', 'Labor Day', NULL, NULL, 'labor-day-discount-codes', 'Labor Day Event – Hot Savings & Holiday Deals!', 'Labor Day event, Labor Day deals, holiday discounts, Labor Day sales, special offers, Labor Day shopping, best Labor Day promotions', 'Celebrate the Labor Day Event with massive savings! Shop exclusive holiday deals, hot discounts, and special offers you won’t want to miss.', 'uploads/1763234644.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234495.jpg', NULL, 'Celebrate hard work with savings! 💼 Top Code Voucher brings you Labor Day coupons and deals on electronics, fashion, and home essentials.', 'Labor Day isn’t just a holiday — it’s a chance to save big! Top Code Voucher helps you find Labor Day discounts across multiple categories.\r\n\r\n* Savings on appliances, furniture, and decor\r\n* Deals on clothing, electronics, and travel\r\n* Verified coupon codes and flash sales\r\n\r\nEnjoy your long weekend and shop smarter with Labor Day Deals at Top Code Voucher.', 1, 0, 19, '2025-10-03 16:53:27', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(19, NULL, 10, 'Cyber Monday Event', 'Cyber Monday', NULL, NULL, 'cyber-monday-deals', 'Cyber Monday Event – Huge Online Savings Await!', 'Cyber Monday event, Cyber Monday deals, Cyber Monday sales, online discounts, Cyber Monday shopping, exclusive Cyber Monday offers, Cyber Monday savings', 'Shop the Cyber Monday Event for unbeatable online discounts! Grab exclusive deals on tech, fashion, and more before these limited-time offers vanish.', 'uploads/1763234617.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234543.jpg', NULL, 'Cyber Monday means online shopping at its best! 🖥️ Save big with exclusive Cyber Monday coupon codes from top online stores at Top Code Voucher.', 'Cyber Monday is the biggest online shopping day of the year, and Top Code Voucher brings you massive savings across electronics, gadgets, fashion, and more.\r\n\r\n* Online-exclusive discounts\r\n* Verified codes & flash deals\r\n* Updated daily with new offers\r\n\r\nShop smarter this Cyber Monday with Top Code Voucher.', 1, 0, 28, '2025-10-03 18:09:36', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(20, NULL, 11, 'Mother\'s Day Event Deals', 'Mothers Day', NULL, NULL, 'mothers-day-codes', 'Mother\'s Day Vouchers Event – Surprise Her with Deals!', 'Mother\'s Day vouchers, Mother\'s Day deals, Mother\'s Day discounts, Mother\'s Day event, gift vouchers Mother\'s Day, Mother\'s Day special offers', 'Celebrate with the Mother’s Day Vouchers Event! Unlock special discounts, gift ideas, and exclusive offers to make her day extra special and unforgettable.', 'uploads/1763234598.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234584.jpg', NULL, 'Show love to Mom with savings! 🌷 Top Code Voucher offers Mother’s Day coupons on gifts, flowers, jewelry, and more.', 'Celebrate your mom without overspending — Top Code Voucher brings you Mother’s Day discount codes for flowers, chocolates, personalized gifts, and more.\r\n\r\n* Savings on thoughtful presents\r\n* Verified deals from popular stores\r\n* Updated daily', 1, 0, 22, '2025-10-03 18:46:36', '2025-11-18 10:24:12'),
(21, NULL, 12, 'Father\'s Day Event', 'Fathers Day', NULL, NULL, 'fathers-day-coupons-codes', 'Father\'s Day Event – Gifts, Vouchers & Hot Discounts', 'Father\'s Day event, Father\'s Day vouchers, Father\'s Day discounts, Father\'s Day gifts, Father\'s Day deals, Father\'s Day special offers', 'Celebrate Father’s Day Event with exclusive vouchers, top discounts, and gift deals to surprise dad. Shop smart and make his special day unforgettable!', 'uploads/1763234767.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234697.jpg', NULL, 'Celebrate Dad with discounts! 🎁 Top Code Voucher offers Father’s Day coupons for gadgets, fashion, and gifts.', 'Father’s Day is a wonderful occasion to show appreciation for the man who has always been there for you. Whether it’s gadgets, tools, stylish apparel, or personalized gifts, finding the perfect present doesn’t have to be expensive. With Top Code Voucher’s exclusive Father’s Day coupon codes and discount deals, you can shop top brands while keeping your budget in check.\r\n\r\nFrom smart electronics to everyday essentials, our curated vouchers ensure you’ll find meaningful gifts at unbeatable prices. Celebrate your dad in style this Father’s Day and enjoy the joy of giving—without overspending.', 1, 0, 20, '2025-10-03 21:03:43', '2025-11-18 10:24:13'),
(22, NULL, 13, 'New Year Deals', 'New Year', NULL, NULL, 'new-year-deals', 'New Year Deals 2025 | Best Coupons & Discount Codes – Top Code Voucher', 'new year deals 2026, new year coupons, new year discount codes, holiday deals, january sale coupons, new year shopping offers, online promo codes, fashion new year sale, electronics new year discounts, Top Code Voucher', 'Kickstart the New Year with massive savings! Explore Top Code Voucher’s exclusive New Year deals, coupons, and discount codes on fashion, electronics, travel, food, and more.', 'uploads/1763234753.webp', NULL, 'uploads/1763234733.jpg', NULL, 'Start the year with savings! 🎊 Top Code Voucher brings you New Year coupon codes and deals to kick off 2026 the smart way.', 'Ring in the New Year with fresh discounts from Top Code Voucher. From fashion to travel, tech to gifts, we’ve got coupons to make your start of the year budget-friendly.\r\n\r\n* Discounts across all categories\r\n* Verified codes & daily updates\r\n* Great savings for a fresh start', 1, 1, 20, '2025-10-03 23:45:40', '2025-11-18 10:24:13'),
