(141, NULL, 7, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 66, 1, 'Abbode Us', 'https://shopabbode.com/', 'uploads/1758655365.webp', 'https://shopabbode.com/', 'https://shopabbode.com/', 'https://shopabbode.com/', 'https://shopabbode.com/', NULL, NULL, 'Finding the perfect Abbode coupon code can make your custom embroidery dreams more affordable while accessing this NYC-based brand’s unique collection of personalized home goods, apparel, and one-of-a-kind embroidered pieces. Abbode specializes in modern embroidery featuring exclusive home goods, apparel, and one of a kind pieces made with love from NYC, making their promotional offers particularly valuable for customers seeking personalized gifts and custom designs.', 'Abbode offers custom embroidery services for any occasion, from heartfelt gifts to personalized keepsakes, with beautifully crafted products ready to ship or customizable to your preferences. Their unique position in the custom embroidery market means that coupon codes provide exceptional value when investing in personalized items that typically command premium pricing.', '<h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3><h4>1. Where can I find current Abbode coupon codes?</h4><p>The best sources for current Abbode coupon codes are their official website, email newsletter, and verified social media accounts. These channels provide authentic codes with clear terms and expiration dates.</p><h4>2. Do Abbode coupon codes work on custom embroidery services?</h4><p>Most Abbode promotional codes apply to both ready-to-ship items and custom embroidery services, though some restrictions may apply to rush orders or specific customization options. Check individual code terms for details.</p><h4>3. Can I use multiple Abbode coupon codes on one order?</h4><p>Typically, only one coupon code can be applied per order, though some special promotions may allow combining manufacturer codes with other offers. Always check the specific terms and conditions for each code.</p><h4>4. How long do Abbode coupon codes usually last?</h4><p>Validity periods vary from 24-hour flash sales to month-long seasonal promotions. Holiday and special event codes often have extended validity to accommodate gift-giving timelines and custom order processing.</p><h4>5. What should I do if my Abbode coupon code isn’t working?</h4><p>First, verify the code spelling and expiration date, then ensure your cart meets any minimum purchase requirements. If problems persist with a valid code, contact Abbode’s customer service team for assistance.</p>', NULL, 'abbode-us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uploads/1758655365.webp', '2025-09-23 17:18:46', '2025-11-12 16:32:23'),
(142, NULL, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 56, 1, '2Modern Us', 'https://www.2modern.com/', 'uploads/1758648522.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Explore modern furniture and contemporary lighting at 2Modern, your destination for stylish, design-driven interiors. Shop top brands in modern sofas, dining tables, pendant lights, and home décor. With curated collections and sustainable options, 2Modern helps you create timeless spaces that... Read More', 'Explore modern furniture and contemporary lighting at 2Modern, your destination for stylish, design-driven interiors. Shop top brands in modern sofas, dining tables, pendant lights, and home décor. With curated collections and sustainable options, 2Modern helps you create timeless spaces that... Read More', '<h3>Types of Available Discounts</h3><p><strong>Percentage-based savings</strong>&nbsp;are most common, typically offering 10-25% off total purchases. These work exceptionally well for larger items like dining sets or sectional sofas.</p><p><strong>Free shipping codes</strong>&nbsp;provide substantial value given furniture shipping costs. These promotions often activate on orders over $99-$199, potentially saving hundreds on delivery fees.</p><p><strong>Category-specific promotions</strong>&nbsp;frequently target popular sections.&nbsp;<strong>2Modern lighting</strong>&nbsp;enthusiasts should watch for deals on pendant lights, floor lamps, and designer fixtures.</p>', NULL, '2modern-us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uploads/1758648522.webp', '2025-09-23 17:28:42', '2025-11-18 10:24:03'),
(143, NULL, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 61, 1, '4seating', 'https://4seating.com/', 'uploads/1758648801.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, '4seating specializes in premium home theater seating, sectionals, and recliners designed for ultimate comfort and style. With customizable options, top-quality materials, and modern designs, 4seating enhances your entertainment space. Shop luxury theater chairs, sofas, and accessories that combine... Read More', '4seating specializes in premium home theater seating, sectionals, and recliners designed for ultimate comfort and style. With customizable options, top-quality materials, and modern designs, 4seating enhances your entertainment space. Shop luxury theater chairs, sofas, and accessories that combine... Read More', '<p>4seating specializes in premium home theater seating, sectionals, and recliners designed for ultimate comfort and style. With customizable options, top-quality materials, and modern designs, 4seating enhances your entertainment space. Shop luxury theater chairs, sofas, and accessories that combine...&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(26, 177, 183);\">Read More</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', NULL, '4seating', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uploads/1758989093.webp', '2025-09-23 17:33:21', '2025-11-12 16:31:31'),
(144, NULL, 4, 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 79, 1, 'Japspeed Uk', 'https://www.japspeed.co.uk/', 'uploads/1758649126.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Japspeed is a performance automotive parts brand specializing in high-quality upgrades for Japanese cars. Known for exhausts, manifolds, coilovers, intercoolers, and racing accessories, Japspeed products enhance speed, handling, and reliability. Trusted by motorsport enthusiasts and tuners,... Read More', 'Japspeed is a performance automotive parts brand specializing in high-quality upgrades for Japanese cars. Known for exhausts, manifolds, coilovers, intercoolers, and racing accessories, Japspeed products enhance speed, handling, and reliability. Trusted by motorsport enthusiasts and tuners,... Read More', '<h5>1. Where can I find current Japspeed discount codes?</h5><p>The most reliable sources for Japspeed discount codes are their official website, authorized UK dealers like SPD Automotive, and verified social media accounts. Always verify code authenticity to ensure warranty coverage and genuine parts quality.</p><h5>2. Do Japspeed discount codes work on all product categories?</h5><p>Most promotional codes apply across their full catalog, though some restrictions may apply to newest products or special order items. Performance parts like exhaust systems and suspension components frequently offer the highest savings potential.</p><h5>3. Can I combine Japspeed discount codes with dealer promotions?</h5><p>Policies vary by retailer, but some authorized dealers allow combining manufacturer codes with their own promotional pricing. Check specific terms and conditions for each discount opportunity before purchase.</p><h5>4. How much can I typically save with Japspeed discount codes?</h5><p>Savings generally range from 10-25% off regular prices, with seasonal promotions and bulk orders sometimes offering deeper discounts. High-value performance parts often provide the greatest dollar savings through percentage-based codes.</p><h5>5. Do discount codes affect Japspeed warranty coverage?</h5><p>Legitimate discount codes from authorized sources do not compromise warranty coverage or parts authenticity. Japspeed maintains full warranty support regardless of promotional pricing used during purchase from verified dealers.</p>', NULL, 'japspeed-uk', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uploads/1758649126.webp', '2025-09-23 17:38:46', '2025-11-12 16:31:17'),
(145, NULL, 3, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 52, 1, 'Eonon Us', 'https://www.eonon.com/', 'uploads/1758649538.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Eonon offers premium car multimedia systems, Android head units, and smart navigation solutions designed for modern vehicles. With advanced features, seamless connectivity, and high-quality audio, Eonon products enhance driving comfort and entertainment. Explore affordable in-dash units, car stereos, and accessories trusted worldwide for performance, reliability, and cutting-edge automotive technology. Show Less', 'Eonon offers premium car multimedia systems, Android head units, and smart navigation solutions designed for modern vehicles. With advanced features, seamless connectivity, and high-quality audio, Eonon products enhance driving comfort and entertainment. Explore affordable in-dash units, car stereos, and accessories trusted worldwide for performance, reliability, and cutting-edge automotive technology. Show Less', '<p>Eonon offers premium car multimedia systems, Android head units, and smart navigation solutions designed for modern vehicles. With advanced features, seamless connectivity, and high-quality audio, Eonon products enhance driving comfort and entertainment. Explore affordable in-dash units, car stereos, and accessories trusted worldwide for performance, reliability, and cutting-edge automotive technology.&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(26, 177, 183);\">Show Less</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', NULL, 'eonon-us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uploads/1758649538.webp', '2025-09-23 17:45:38', '2025-11-12 16:26:35'),
