(184, NULL, 45, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 68, 1, 'Next Base', 'https://nextbase.co.uk/', 'uploads/1759264780.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Protecting your vehicle and ensuring peace of mind on the road doesn\'t have to drain your wallet. A Nextbase discount code can help you save substantially on premium dash cams, rear-view cameras, and essential car accessories from the UK\'s leading dash cam manufacturer. Whether you\'re looking to upgrade your vehicle\'s security, document your journeys, or simply want evidence in case of an accident, finding the right promotional offer makes investing in quality recording technology more affordable than ever.', 'Nextbase has established itself as Britain\'s number one dash cam brand, trusted by millions of drivers across the UK and beyond. The company\'s innovative product range includes front-facing dash cams, dual-camera systems with rear-view capabilities, 4K ultra-high-definition recorders, and intelligent cameras with Alexa integration and emergency SOS features. Their technology incorporates advanced features like GPS tracking, WiFi connectivity, parking mode surveillance, and night vision capabilities that deliver crystal-clear footage in any lighting condition.', '<p><strong>Can I use multiple discount codes on one order?</strong> </p><p>Typically, Nextbase allows only one promotional code per transaction. Choose the voucher that provides the greatest savings for your particular basket contents.</p><p><strong>Do Nextbase vouchers work on all camera models?</strong> </p><p>While many codes apply across the entire range, some exclude new releases, premium models like the iQ, or already-discounted products. Always check the terms and conditions.</p><p><strong>How often does Nextbase release new promotional codes?</strong> </p><p>New discount codes typically appear monthly, with increased frequency during holiday seasons, new product launches, and major retail events.</p><p><strong>Can I return items purchased with a discount code?</strong> </p><p>Yes, standard return policies apply to discounted purchases, though refunds will reflect the actual price paid after discount application.</p>', 'Next Base Discount Code: Save More on Dash Cams Today!', 'next-base', 'Next Base Discount Code: Save More on Dash Cams Today!', 'Grab the latest Next Base discount code and enjoy big savings on dash cams, car accessories, and safety tech. Drive smarter with deals you can’t miss!', NULL, NULL, 'Next Base discount code, Next Base promo code, Next Base coupon, Next Base voucher, dash cam discount, car tech deals, Next Base savings  Select 77 more words to run Humanizer.', NULL, '2025-09-30 20:39:40', '2025-11-12 16:58:19'),
(185, NULL, 46, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 34, 1, 'Juicy Details', 'https://www.juicy-details.co.uk/', 'uploads/1759265177.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Keeping your vehicle looking showroom-fresh shouldn\'t require a showroom-sized budget. A Juicy Details discount code can help you save significantly on professional-grade car care products, detailing supplies, and cleaning solutions that deliver exceptional results. Whether you\'re a detailing enthusiast, professional valeter, or simply someone who takes pride in maintaining their vehicle\'s appearance, finding the right promotional offer makes accessing premium automotive care products more affordable while ensuring outstanding results every time.', 'Juicy Details has carved out a reputation as a premium supplier of professional car detailing products and automotive care solutions across the United Kingdom. Their extensive product catalogue includes everything from pH-neutral car shampoos and snow foam pre-wash solutions to ceramic coatings, paint correction compounds, and microfiber towels. The brand specializes in high-quality formulations that deliver professional results without harsh chemicals that can damage paintwork, trim, or interior surfaces.\r\n\r\nWhat sets Juicy Details apart is their commitment to offering products that work for both enthusiasts and professionals. Their range covers exterior detailing products like waxes, sealants, and quick detailers, interior care solutions including leather cleaners and fabric protectors, and specialist items such as wheel cleaners, tire dressings, and glass treatments. When you apply a Juicy Details discount code to your purchase, you\'re accessing professional-grade detailing products at consumer-friendly prices, ensuring your vehicle receives the care it deserves without breaking the bank.', '<p><strong>Can I use multiple promotional codes on a single order?</strong> </p><p>Most retailers, including Juicy Details, permit only one discount code per transaction. Select the voucher offering the greatest savings for your specific basket contents.</p><p><strong>Do discount codes work on all products?</strong> </p><p>While many codes apply site-wide, some exclude certain premium brands, new releases, or already-discounted items. Always review the terms and conditions associated with each promotional offer.</p><p><strong>How long do Juicy Details vouchers remain valid?</strong> </p><p>Most promotional codes have expiration dates ranging from a few days for flash sales to several weeks for seasonal promotions. Use codes promptly to avoid missing savings opportunities.</p><p><strong>Can I return products purchased with a discount code?</strong> </p><p>Yes, standard return policies apply to all purchases regardless of whether a discount code was used. Refunds will reflect the actual discounted price paid.</p>', 'Juicy Details Discount Code – Shine & Save Big Today!', 'juicy-details', 'Juicy Details Discount Code – Shine & Save Big Today!', 'Unlock the Juicy Details discount code for huge savings on premium car cleaning products. Get spotless results while keeping more cash in your pocket!', NULL, NULL, 'Juicy Details discount code, Juicy Details promo code, Juicy Details voucher, Juicy Details coupon, car cleaning discount, detailing deals, Juicy Details savings', NULL, '2025-09-30 20:46:17', '2025-11-04 08:12:45'),
(186, NULL, 47, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 28, 1, 'Doona', 'https://doona.shop/', 'uploads/1759336487.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Investing in your baby\'s safety and convenience doesn\'t have to stretch your parenting budget. A Doona discount code can help you save substantially on the revolutionary car seat stroller combination and other innovative baby travel products that make life easier for modern parents. Whether you\'re preparing for your first baby, upgrading your travel gear, or looking for the perfect gift for new parents, finding the right promotional offer makes accessing this award-winning baby equipment more affordable while ensuring your little one travels in comfort and safety.', 'Doona has transformed the baby travel industry with its groundbreaking infant car seat stroller design that seamlessly converts from car seat to stroller in seconds. This innovative product eliminates the need for separate car seats and stroller frames, making it perfect for parents who value convenience, urban families navigating public transport, and anyone who frequently travels by taxi or rideshare. The Doona car seat meets rigorous safety standards including ECE R44/04 certification and has won numerous awards for innovation and design excellence.', '<p><strong>Can I use multiple discount codes on one Doona purchase?</strong> </p><p>Most retailers permit only one promotional code per transaction. Select the voucher offering the greatest savings for your specific basket contents and consider whether percentage or fixed-amount codes provide better value.</p><p><strong>Do discount codes work on all Doona colors and editions?</strong> </p><p>While many codes apply across the range, some exclude new releases, limited editions, or already-discounted items. Always review the terms and conditions to understand any restrictions.</p><p><strong>Will using a discount code affect my product warranty?</strong> </p><p>No, purchasing from authorized retailers with discount codes does not impact your Doona product warranty. However, buying from unauthorized sellers or non-approved websites may void warranties regardless of price.</p><p><strong>How often do new Doona promotional codes become available?</strong> </p><p>New discount codes typically appear monthly through authorized retailers, with increased frequency during major shopping holidays, new collection launches, and seasonal clearance periods.</p>', 'Doona Discount Code – Save Big on Baby Gear Today', 'doona', 'Doona Discount Code – Save Big on Baby Gear Today', 'Grab the latest Doona discount code and enjoy huge savings on strollers, car seats, and baby gear. Shop smart and save more with exclusive Doona offers.', NULL, NULL, 'Doona discount code, Doona promo code, Doona voucher, Doona offers, Doona baby gear deals, Doona stroller discount, Doona car seat coupon', NULL, '2025-10-01 16:34:47', '2025-11-03 23:03:33'),
(187, NULL, 48, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 76, 1, 'Samsung', 'https://www.samsung.com/', 'uploads/1759337081.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Looking for a Samsung discount code to slash prices on your next Galaxy smartphone, Smart TV, or home appliance? You\'re in the right place. With Samsung\'s premium product lineup and strategic promotional calendar, savvy shoppers can save hundreds of dollars using the right coupon codes, promo deals, and seasonal offers.', 'Finding genuine Samsung promo codes requires knowing where to look. The official Samsung website regularly features exclusive promotional offers, especially during major shopping events like Black Friday, Cyber Monday, and back-to-school season. Sign up for Samsung\'s email newsletter to receive subscriber-only coupon codes sent directly to your inbox.\r\n\r\nRetailer partnerships also provide significant savings opportunities. Major electronics retailers like Best Buy, Amazon, and Walmart frequently offer Samsung-specific promotional codes that stack with manufacturer rebates. Student discount programs through Samsung Education Store provide up to 30% off on select Galaxy devices and laptops.', '<p><strong>Can I use multiple Samsung promo codes on one order?</strong></p><p>Generally, Samsung limits checkout to one discount code per transaction, though you can often combine a promo code with trade-in credits, Samsung Rewards points, or manufacturer rebates.</p><p><strong>Do Samsung discount codes work on already-discounted items?</strong></p><p>Most promotional codes exclude clearance items and products already marked down. However, site-wide percentage codes during major sales events may apply to sale prices—always test at checkout.</p><p><strong>How often does Samsung release new discount codes?</strong></p><p>Samsung updates promotional offers weekly, with major code releases aligning with product launches, holidays, and seasonal shopping events throughout the year.</p><p><strong>Are Samsung Education Store discounts better than regular promo codes?</strong></p><p>Student discounts typically provide 20-30% savings year-round, often exceeding limited-time promo codes. Education pricing also stacks with seasonal promotions for maximum savings.</p>', 'Samsung Discount Code – Unlock Big Savings Today', 'samsung', 'Samsung Discount Code – Unlock Big Savings Today', 'Use the latest Samsung discount code to save on phones, TVs, and electronics. Get exclusive Samsung offers and shop your favorite gadgets for less.', NULL, NULL, 'Samsung discount code, Samsung promo code, Samsung voucher, Samsung coupon, Samsung deals, Samsung offers, Samsung phone discount, Samsung TV code  Select 80 more words to run Humanizer.', NULL, '2025-10-01 16:44:41', '2025-11-12 16:45:52'),
