checkout.</p><p><strong>How often does H&amp;M release new discount codes?</strong></p><p>H&amp;M updates promotional offers bi-weekly, with major code releases aligning with fashion season transitions, holidays, and special shopping events like Singles\' Day and Black Friday.</p><p><strong>Does H&amp;M offer a first-purchase discount?</strong></p><p>New email subscribers typically receive a welcome voucher offering 10-25% off their first online order within 30 days of signup.</p>', 'H&M Discount Code – Shop Fashion Deals & Save Big', 'hm', 'H&M Discount Code – Shop Fashion Deals & Save Big', 'Grab the latest H&M discount code to save on trendy clothing, shoes, and accessories. Shop your favorite H&M fashion picks now with exclusive savings.', NULL, NULL, 'H&M discount code, H&M promo code, H&M voucher, H&M coupon, H&M deals, H&M offers, H&M clothing discount, H&M fashion code', NULL, '2025-10-01 16:55:56', '2025-11-03 22:40:51'),
(189, NULL, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 34, 1, 'Baby MORI', 'https://babymori.com/', 'uploads/1759342195.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Looking for a Baby MORI discount code to save on luxurious bamboo sleepwear and organic baby essentials? You\'ve discovered the ultimate resource for accessing exclusive promo codes, seasonal promotions, and insider strategies that help parents save 15-40% on MORI\'s award-winning baby products. From signature zip-up sleepsuits to temperature-regulating blankets, the right voucher code makes premium quality affordable.', 'Securing genuine Baby MORI promo codes starts with knowing the most reliable sources. MORI\'s official newsletter delivers subscriber-exclusive voucher codes directly to your inbox, often featuring first-access to seasonal sales and new parent welcome discounts of 10-15% off your first order.\r\nThe Baby MORI website homepage prominently displays current promotional banners during major shopping events. Parents can also access special offers through MORI\'s mobile app, which occasionally features app-only flash sales and exclusive discount bundles.\r\nPartnership platforms like Emma\'s Diary, Bounty, and NCT provide verified parent discount codes through their pregnancy and parenting programs. These collaborations often stack new parent discounts with seasonal promotions for maximum savings on essential baby items.', '<p><strong>Can I combine multiple Baby MORI promo codes?</strong> </p><p>MORI\'s checkout system accepts one discount code per transaction, though you can combine a promo code with loyalty points redemption or gift card payment for enhanced savings.</p><p><strong>Do Baby MORI discount codes work on sale items?</strong> </p><p>Standard promotional codes typically exclude sale items, but major shopping events like Black Friday feature sitewide codes that apply to already-discounted products—always check specific terms.</p><p><strong>How often does Baby MORI release new discount codes?</strong> </p><p>MORI updates promotional offers monthly, with major code releases during seasonal transitions, holidays, and special shopping events like Singles\' Day and Cyber Week.</p><p><strong>Does Baby MORI offer a first-time buyer discount?</strong> </p><p>New newsletter subscribers commonly receive a welcome voucher offering 10-15% off their first order, valid for 30 days after signup.</p><p><strong>Are Baby MORI discount codes valid internationally?</strong> </p><p>Code validity varies by region. UK-issued codes work for UK deliveries, while US and EU markets receive region-specific promotional offers through their respective websites.</p>', NULL, 'baby-mori', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-01 18:09:55', '2025-11-05 14:49:50'),
(190, NULL, 51, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 22, 1, 'Yours Clothing', 'https://www.yoursclothing.co.uk/', 'uploads/1759343620.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Searching for a Yours Clothing discount code to refresh your wardrobe with stylish plus-size fashion? You\'ve found the definitive guide to accessing exclusive promo codes, seasonal promotions, and money-saving strategies that help you save 20-50% on trendy clothing from the UK\'s leading curve fashion retailer. From everyday essentials to special occasion outfits, the right voucher code transforms your shopping experience', 'The most reliable Yours Clothing promo codes come from trusted official sources. Subscribe to the Yours Clothing newsletter to receive exclusive voucher codes delivered straight to your inbox, often featuring subscriber-only deals offering 15-25% off before public release.\r\nThe Yours Clothing website homepage displays current promotional banners prominently, especially during major sales events. Download the Yours Clothing mobile app for app-exclusive discount offers, early access to flash sales, and push notifications about surprise code drops.\r\nYours Clothing maintains an active presence on social media platforms including Facebook, Instagram, and TikTok, where they occasionally share limited-time promo codes during influencer collaborations and seasonal campaigns. Loyalty program members receive birthday vouchers and exclusive member-only discount codes throughout the year.\r\nStudent discount platforms like Student Beans provide verified students with year-round savings, while employee discount schemes through Blue Light Card and Health Service Discounts offer special ra', '<p><strong>Can I use multiple Yours Clothing promo codes on one order?</strong> </p><p>Yours Clothing\'s checkout system accepts only one discount code per transaction, though you can combine a voucher with loyalty points redemption and multi-buy promotional offers for enhanced savings.</p><p><strong>Do Yours Clothing discount codes work on sale items?</strong> </p><p>Standard promotional codes typically apply to full-price merchandise only, but special sitewide event codes during Black Friday, Cyber Monday, and major holidays may include already-discounted sale items—always verify terms.</p><p><strong>How often does Yours Clothing release new discount codes?</strong> </p><p>Yours Clothing updates promotional offers weekly, with major voucher releases aligning with payday weekends, seasonal transitions, and national shopping events throughout the year.</p><p><strong>Does Yours Clothing offer a first-time buyer discount?</strong> </p><p>New newsletter subscribers frequently receive a welcome voucher offering 15-20% off their first online order, valid for 30 days after email subscription signup.</p><p><strong>Are Yours Clothing discount codes valid in-store?</strong> </p><p>Most online promotional codes don\'t transfer to physical stores, though in-store shoppers access different advantages including same-day markdowns, store-exclusive promotions, and immediate loyalty point application at checkout.</p>', 'Yours Clothing Discount Code – Plus Size Fashion Deals', 'yours-clothing', 'Yours Clothing Discount Code – Plus Size Fashion Deals', 'Grab the latest Yours Clothing discount code and save big on stylish plus-size fashion. Shop trendy dresses, tops, and essentials at unbeatable prices today!', NULL, NULL, 'Yours Clothing discount code, Yours Clothing promo code, Yours Clothing coupon, Yours Clothing voucher, Yours Clothing deals, Yours Clothing offers, plus size fashion discount', NULL, '2025-10-01 18:33:40', '2025-11-03 21:30:16'),
