(208, NULL, 69, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 35, 1, 'MeasureUp', 'https://partners.measureup.com/c?c=39525&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1759873479.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'MeasureUp is a trusted leader in IT certification practice tests and exam preparation, helping professionals succeed in Microsoft, CompTIA, Cisco, AWS, and other industry-standard certifications. Our high-quality, exam-aligned practice tests and assessments are designed to boost confidence, reinforce learning, and ensure real exam readiness. With detailed explanations, performance tracking, and customizable study modes, MeasureUp empowers learners to master technical skills and pass their certification exams on the first try. Whether you\'re advancing your IT career or upskilling your team, MeasureUp provides reliable, expert-crafted resources trusted by educators, enterprises, and certification bodies worldwide. Prepare smarter—choose MeasureUp for guaranteed success.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'measureup', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-07 21:44:39', '2025-11-03 21:17:07'),
(209, NULL, 70, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 22, 1, 'Mercury Holidays', 'https://ttcdn.mercuryholidays.co.uk/c?c=38107&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1759874243.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Mercury Holidays offers exceptional value holiday packages, escorted tours, and all-inclusive getaways to top destinations worldwide. From beach holidays in Malta, Spain, and the Canary Islands to guided cultural tours in India, Sri Lanka, and Vietnam, Mercury Holidays combines quality, affordability, and expertise. With over 40 years of experience, we provide ATOL-protected holidays with flexible booking options and expert customer service. Whether you\'re looking for last-minute deals, solo travel packages, or luxury escapes, Mercury Holidays has the perfect trip for you. Discover unbeatable prices on dream holidays and experience the world for less with a trusted UK travel provider.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'mercury-holidays', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-07 21:57:23', '2025-11-03 15:42:33'),
(210, NULL, 71, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 27, 1, 'My outdoor Kitchen', 'https://tc.tradetracker.net/?c=39226&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1759946331.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'My Outdoor Kitchen transforms your backyard into a gourmet paradise. Whether you\'re grilling, entertaining, or enjoying family time, our premium outdoor kitchen solutions bring style, function, and durability. Choose from built-in BBQs, weatherproof cabinets, countertops, sinks, and pizza ovens tailored to your space. Ideal for summer parties or year-round cooking, our custom designs fit any layout and lifestyle. Built with high-quality materials like stainless steel and stone, My Outdoor Kitchen blends seamlessly into your outdoor living area. Discover the perfect balance of performance and aesthetics. Elevate your outdoor cooking experience—explore our collections today!', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'my-outdoor-kitchen', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-08 17:58:51', '2025-11-03 21:40:03'),
(211, NULL, 72, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 24, 1, 'Tennis Ticketing', 'https://tennisticketing.com/tennistt/?tt=39674_12_496844_&r=', 'uploads/1760026001.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tennis Ticketing refers to the process of selling and managing tickets for tennis matches and tournaments. This includes online and offline platforms where fans can purchase tickets to watch live events like Wimbledon, US Open, or local club matches. Modern tennis ticketing systems offer features like seat selection, digital ticket delivery, mobile scanning, and real-time availability updates. Many tournaments use dynamic pricing based on demand. Secure payment options and customer support are essential parts of the system. Tennis ticketing also helps organizers track attendance, manage crowd flow, and enhance the overall spectator experience. Efficient ticketing boosts sales and fan satisfaction.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'tennis-ticketing', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-09 16:06:41', '2025-11-04 12:33:18'),
(212, NULL, 73, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 42, 1, 'Sleep Aids', 'https://deals.sleepaids.com/c?c=39511&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1760026794.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Sleep Aids are products or techniques designed to help individuals fall asleep faster and improve sleep quality. Common sleep aids include melatonin supplements, herbal remedies like valerian root, prescription medications, white noise machines, and weighted blankets. Natural sleep aids promote relaxation and support a healthy sleep cycle. Many people use sleep aids to manage insomnia, jet lag, or stress-related sleep issues. It’s important to choose safe, non-habit-forming options. Optimizing your sleep environment, limiting screen time, and maintaining a bedtime routine can also enhance sleep. Quality sleep aids support overall health, mental clarity, and daytime energy, contributing to better well-being.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'sleep-aids', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-09 16:19:54', '2025-11-03 21:29:33'),
(213, NULL, 74, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 46, 1, 'Regency Chess IE', 'https://tc.tradetracker.net/?c=38863&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1760035590.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Regency Chess is a premium online retailer specializing in high-quality chess sets, boards, and accessories. Known for its craftsmanship and elegant designs, Regency Chess offers a wide selection of Staunton chess sets, luxury wooden boards, and handcrafted pieces made from rosewood, ebony, and boxwood. Ideal for collectors, enthusiasts, and tournament players, each product combines aesthetic appeal with practical functionality. Regency Chess also provides themed sets, travel chess sets, and digital clocks. With secure shipping, excellent customer service, and competitive prices, RegencyChess.com is a trusted destination for quality chess products in the UK and internationally. Perfect for gifts, clubs, or personal use.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'regency-chess-ie', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-09 18:46:30', '2025-11-04 11:21:42'),
(214, NULL, 75, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 34, 1, 'Musement', 'https://tc.tradetracker.net/?c=32134&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1760051505.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Musement is a leading online platform that allows travelers to discover and book tours, activities, and attractions worldwide. From skip-the-line museum tickets and guided city tours to food experiences and cultural events, Musement connects users with curated local experiences in top travel destinations. With real-time availability, mobile-friendly booking, and secure payments, it offers a seamless way to plan trips. Whether you\'re exploring Rome, Paris, New York, or Tokyo, Musement enhances your journey with personalized recommendations and insider tips. Ideal for tourists seeking convenience and authenticity, Musement helps you make the most of every destination with trusted, high-quality travel experiences.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'musement', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-09 23:03:57', '2025-11-18 10:24:11'),
(215, NULL, 76, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 16, 1, 'Perfume Plus Direct', 'https://www.perfumeplusdirect.co.uk/perfume/?tt=26803_12_496844_&r=', 'uploads/1760390574.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Perfume Plus Direct is your go-to online destination for authentic designer fragrances at unbeatable prices. We specialize in premium perfumes for men and women, offering a wide selection from top brands like Dior, Chanel, Gucci, and more. Whether you\'re looking for a signature scent or the perfect gift, Perfume Plus Direct delivers fast, reliable service and genuine products every time. Enjoy seasonal deals, exclusive discounts, and new arrivals updated regularly. With secure checkout and exceptional customer support, shopping for fragrances has never been easier. Discover luxury perfumes with confidence at Perfume Plus Direct — where quality and value meet.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'perfume-plus-direct', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-13 21:22:54', '2025-11-02 15:26:39'),
(216, NULL, 77, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 41, 1, 'Pinn Tech', 'https://www.pinntech.co.uk/hardware/?tt=30836_12_496844_&r=%2F', 'uploads/1760391375.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'PinnTech is a leading provider of innovative technology solutions, specializing in IT services, cybersecurity, cloud computing, and digital transformation. We empower businesses with scalable tech strategies that enhance efficiency, security, and growth. At PinnTech, our expert team delivers customized IT support, managed services, and cutting-edge solutions tailored to your industry needs. Whether you\'re a small business or enterprise, we ensure seamless integration and round-the-clock support. Trusted by clients across various sectors, PinnTech combines technology and insight to drive measurable results. Experience the future of IT with PinnTech — your partner for smart, secure, and scalable technology solutions.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'pinn-tech', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-13 21:36:15', '2025-11-01 15:05:48'),
(217, NULL, 78, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 16, 1, 'Regency Chess', 'https://tc.tradetracker.net/?c=29962&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1760392168.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Regency Chess is a premier online retailer offering luxury chess sets, boards, and pieces crafted from the finest materials. Specializing in Staunton chess sets, tournament boards, and unique themed designs, Regency Chess combines craftsmanship with functionality. Whether you\'re a beginner or a seasoned player, our curated collection includes wooden, magnetic, and travel chess sets to suit every level. With fast shipping, exceptional customer service, and a commitment to quality, Regency Chess is the trusted choice for chess enthusiasts worldwide. Discover elegant designs, handcrafted detail, and timeless strategy — elevate your game with the finest selection at Regency Chess.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'regency-chess', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-13 21:49:28', '2025-11-01 21:31:57'),
(218, NULL, 79, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 25, 1, 'Rent Car', 'https://tc.tradetracker.net/?c=32770&m=12&a=496844&r=&u=', 'uploads/1760393196.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 53, 53, 'Rent Cars UK offers reliable, affordable car hire services across the United Kingdom, catering to both short-term rentals and long-term leasing needs. With a wide fleet of vehicles including economy cars, SUVs, luxury models, and vans, we make travel easy and convenient for every customer. Whether you\'re planning a road trip, business travel, or airport pickup, Rent Cars UK ensures competitive prices, flexible booking, and outstanding customer service. All vehicles are fully insured and maintained to the highest standards. Book online quickly and securely for instant confirmation. Experience hassle-free car rental across the UK with Rent Cars UK today.', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'rent-car', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-10-13 22:06:36', '2025-11-04 05:40:07');
